data.eml:eml: Gadigaleyrodes froggatti, a new genus and species of whitefly (Hemiptera: Aleyrodidae) from Australia

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Dooley Iii, John W., Gillespie, Peter (2013): Gadigaleyrodes froggatti, a new genus and species of whitefly (Hemiptera: Aleyrodidae) from Australia. Zootaxa 3608 (2): 137-146, DOI: http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.3608.2.4
